Text:
Correct me if I'm wrong, but 720 x 400 is not "Highres".

Standard def is 720 x 480
The lowest "Highdef" is 1280 x 720

Therefore, this aint "Highdef"
The audio isn't synced properly... It lags the video by a second or so...

AUDIO SYNC is way off.
NOT HIGHRES

I would not recommend downloading this copy.
I also had problems with the audio being out of sync. Thanks for the upload though.
